Description
-----------

Enables/Disables the pause when loading a level.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

`com_skipLevelLoadPauseÂ [flag]`

Parameters
----------

-   [flag] - Enables/Disables the pause at level load.
    -   0 - Require the player to click the mouse button to start the level.
    -   1 - After the level finishes loading it is immediately started.

